Hawaiian Airlines Flight Delay Analysis¶

by Gilvan Reis¶

March - 2021

Investigation Overview¶

The main objective of this analysis was to find out what are the main causes of delays on Hawaiian Airlines flights, identifying opportunities for improvements in the company.

Dataset Overview¶

The study was conducted on 20,932 operating records from 17 carriers limited to the US area during 2019. A flight is considered to be delayed when it departs at least 15 minutes later than expected.

Delay Causes¶

There are five delay causes:

  • carrier: due to air carrier (e.g. maintenance or crew problems, aircraft cleaning, baggage loading, fueling, etc.).
  • weather: due to extreme weather.
  • nas: due to National Aviation System (e.g. non-extreme weather conditions, airport operations, heavy traffic volume, and air traffic control).
  • security: due to security (e.g. evacuation of a terminal or concourse, re-boarding of aircraft because of security breach, inoperative screening equipment and/or long lines in excess of 29 minutes at screening areas).
  • late aircraft: due to a previous flight using the same aircraft being late.

Late aircraft is the main cause of delays (36.9%). Security delays are very rare (0.2%).

Delayed Flights by Carrier¶

Hawaiian Airlines has the lowest proportion of delayed flights (11.4%) when compared to other carriers.

Delayed Flights by Month by Carrier¶

Hawaiian Airlines has a very low and consistent proportion of delayed flights throughout the year, with February being the month with the highest proportion of delayed flights.

Delay Cause by Month by Carrier¶

However, when comparing the main cause of delays in each carrier, we can observe different behavior on Hawaiian Airlines. The main cause of its delays is due to carrier.

Flights Delayed due Carrier Problems¶

When looking at the proportion of carrier problems in each carrier, we can see that Hawaiian Airlines differs from the others with a much higher proportion, indicating that there is an opportunity for improvement in this area for the company.
